Class CityManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.management.NotificationBroadcasterSupport
      • rmi.CityManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.management.DynamicMBean, javax.management.NotificationBroadcaster, javax.management.NotificationEmitter, javax.management.NotificationListener, CityManagerDMBean

    public class CityManager
extends javax.management.NotificationBroadcasterSupport
implements javax.management.DynamicMBean, CityManagerDMBean, java.io.Serializable
    This class represent a city manager, it can
    • add a city
    • remove a city
    • return the list of cities
    • search a city with a given name
    • search a city at a position
    • return the list of cities near 10km of the given position
    Author:
    Folabi & Caron & Saval.
